Package com.github.dm.rf.android.translator

Package containing classes defining transformation operations between elements, keys and values.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BooleanTranslator
    This interface defines a translator of boolean values into other boolean values.
    FullBooleanTranslator
    This interface extends BooleanTranslator by adding the reverse translation of the value.
    FullIntTranslator
    This interface extends IntTranslator by adding the reverse translation of the value.
    FullLongTranslator
    This interface extends LongTranslator by adding the reverse translation of the value.
    FullTranslator<I,O>
    This interface extends Translator by adding the reverse translation of the element.
    IntTranslator
    This interface defines a translator of int values into other int values.
    LongTranslator
    This interface defines a translator of long values into other long values.
    ToBooleanTranslator<E>
    This interface defines a translator of elements into boolean values.
    ToIntTranslator<E>
    This interface defines a translator of elements into int values.
    ToLongTranslator<E>
    This interface defines a translator of elements into long values.
    Translator<I,O>
    This interface defines a translator of objects into other objects.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Translators
    Utility class providing helper methods for creating and managing Translator objects.
